Sara Shane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sara_Shane 0 Elaine Hollingsworth (née Sterling) (born May 18, 1928), known by the stage name Sara Shane, is a former actress who starred in film and television in the 1950s and early 1960s. She was born in St. Louis, Missouri.
